<HEADLINE> Tehran Stock Exchange Index Up </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
TEHRAN, January 5 (Xinhua) -- The general price index at
Tehran Stock Exchange on Tuesday closed at 1,526.30 points, up
0.52 points from Monday's finish.
</P>
<P>
A total of 10,816,786 shares exchanged hands in 1,104 deals
and turnover stood at 7.886 billion rials (about 1.3 million
U.S. dollars).
</P>
<P>
Shares of 19 companies made gains while those of 17 others
declined. 
</P>
</TEXT>
