for the ethnic minorities in Kosovo must be recognized within the
framework of respect for the present borders of Yugoslavia.
</P>
<P>
Greece's Deputy Foreign Minister Yiannos Kranidiotis also met
with Markovic, who briefed the Greek official on the latest
developments in Kosovo and his country's positions concerning a
just settlement of the Kosovo problem. 
