<HEADLINE> Iranian Official Escapes Assassination Attempt </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
TEHRAN, January 5 (Xinhua) -- Head of Tehran province's
justice department Ali Razini escaped an assassination attempt on
Tuesday, the Islamic Republic News Agency (IRNA) reported.
