<HEADLINE> China Basketball League Results </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Bayi Rockets bt ZHEJIANG CYCLONE 135-108
</P>
<P>
Beijing Aoshen bt JINAN ARMY PEGASUS 98-81
