upgrades, 249 dollars for non-Microsoft upgrades, and 499 dollars
for new users.
</P>
<P>
Microsoft also announced a series of promotional programs,
including the Office 2000 Technology Guarantee. For customers who
acquire the Office 97 suite or an individual application between
January 1 and the date when Office 2000 becomes available are
eligible to receive the corresponding Office 2000 suite or
application free. 
